==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Limousine liberal
<hw>Li`mou*sine" lib`er*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a
wealthy or well-to-do person of liberal political inclination. It is
sometimes used as a term of contempt for those espousing the cause of
poor people, without having to endure the discomfort that their policies
may inflict on others, such as the lower middle class.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

